</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#D5D4D5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/uistrahdamtheland.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Istrahd Amtheland</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Buffy Bait</span><br> <font color=#000033>(5/17/01 11:08:29 am)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://home.kc.rr.com/istrahd/ist_img.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Lower cha equal better?</span><hr size=1> Yeah - /shrug - I went through this whole thing once before - BUT ...<br>
<br>
here is what I do know - <br>
<br>
With my claws and my sorc. bowl - my cha is 25.  Over the past several days - I just have noticed that my ST and fear are sticking better.  It is just one of theose inherant things to have kinda a feel for how much or how often something resists in certain places.  It just feels more solid is all. <p><center><Table width=550 border=0><tr><td valign=top align=center colspan=2><center><img src="http://www.kerinakreation.com/images/sigs/istsig.jpg" border=0 alt="Guild Leader of Dark Whispers"></center></td></tr><tr><td valign=top align=center><i><font color="red"><b>Istrahd V'Zarovich<b></i><br>58th Defiler<br>Dark Whispers<br></font></td><td valign=middle align=center><font size=-1><i>"I am The Ancient, I am The Land. My beginnings are lost in the darkness of the past. I was the warrior, I was good and just. I thundered across the land like the wrath of a just god, but the war years and the killing years wore down my soul as the wind wears stone into sand." - Strahd Von Zarovich</i></font></td></tr></table></center></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#E5E5E6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/uistrahdamtheland.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Istrahd Amtheland</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Buffy Bait</span><br> <font color=#000033>(5/17/01 11:10:44 am)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://home.kc.rr.com/istrahd/ist_img.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Lower cha equal better?</span><hr size=1> Oh - I am dying for a helot skull helm. Not the most uber stats - but /shrug ...<br>
<br>
